{"tid":812112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長文慎入 有圖，想聽意見","createTime":"2018-09-09T11:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T15:51:58.000Z","uid":199104,"like":1,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b3eab6eb60f1cb9de4356417fbf0a8350513a171","tid":812112,"uid":199104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:32:39.000Z","msg":"前晚同男朋友仲有佢班fd去飲野。<br />\n有個有男朋友既女仔，<br />\n講野又捉住我男朋友隻手，又話咪咩錫晒佢。<br />\n我認我本身係易呷醋，但我都算，咁大家出嚟玩。<br />\n之後我男朋友同個女仔同另一個fd三個一齊玩緊大話骰。<br />\n之後女仔個男朋友話另一個遊戲,<br />\n個女仔話唔玩，<br />\n話要玩埋大話骰,<br />\n然後個男仔係咁話要玩另一個遊戲,<br />\n個女仔都話唔要。<br />\n咁我就同我男朋友講，係囉不用一齊玩果個遊戲， ,點知佢又話唔好，要繼續玩大話骰 (同個女仔)，<br />\n之後個女仔話咁玩喇，話玩果個遊戲，<br />\n然後我男朋友即刻話好。<br />\n咁我當然嬲喇，佢個朋友話玩，they say no ,<br />\n我話玩，he say no,<br />\n人地女朋友話玩即刻say yes .<br />\n我即刻係佢耳邊講佢會唔會太過份？<br />\n我覺得好落自己面，女朋友講佢唔聽，<br />\n人哋女朋友講，佢即刻聽。<br />\n我好肯定調返轉嗰個我係佢，佢一定會話我。<br />\n然後佢就捉左我出去，話咩只係尊重人男朋友，所以個女仔話玩，佢就話玩。<br />\n咁我咪話人地男朋友話玩，你又唔話玩？<br />\n個女話玩，你話玩就係尊重人男朋友？<br />\n咁好喇，我就好嬲，然後我就話佢，佢又係度話可能醉，我就話咁醉左就做咩都得？<br />\n其實原本都只係諗住話下佢，如果佢道個歉，話聽唔到個男仔講，然後攬下我，話返屋企，我一定會算囉。<br />\n點知唔知係咪佢見到佢有既朋友出黎見到我話佢，<br />\n佢好嬲。就話返我，然後好大聲咁樣吼一聲，然後我想走，<br />\n佢<br />\n一<br />\n手<br />\n扯<br />\n爛<br />\n左<br />\n我<br />\n條<br />\n裙，<br />\n成條掉左落地下，好似拍戲咁，<br />\n然後好大力扯我，就係圖中咁，址同拉我行，可以咁瘀，就知幾大力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/192815_1a3ed7e66b05239ded0da33ebfaafede.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F192815_1a3ed7e66b05239ded0da33ebfaafede.png&h=ab98822e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/192816_25511fcbda68093179034d1eb8ecbbb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F192816_25511fcbda68093179034d1eb8ecbbb7.png&h=8cc46412&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/192817_a6776fdb19124cc8fe9462d3e7785685.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F192817_a6776fdb19124cc8fe9462d3e7785685.png&h=34b41929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我幾經掙扎走返入去，但下面咩都無著，得絲襪同打底褲。<br />\n我果一刻醜到想搵洞藏<br />\n之後佢班朋友叫佢同我道歉，<br />\n佢除左衫被我遮住。<br />\n佢第二次再捉我出去，<br />\n我話佢真係好過份，<br />\n我話我接受唔到咁，<br />\n佢話你係咪想分手呀？<br />\n一步一步逼我，<br />\n然後我衝返入間bar 度。<br />\n好，之後返佢家途中，<br />\n佢個fd同我傾計，<br />\n我就傾下喇，<br />\n我只係講返件事，<br />\n點知我男朋友肯定覺得我係人面前數佢，佢好嬲好嬲。<br />\n個樣兇到我好驚<br />\n果時已經凌晨4點幾<br />\n佢返到佢屋企，好大力bang門，一手掉左我袋去沙發，我地無再講過野。<br />\n佢一開始無上床，得我係床，佢打機。<br />\n<br />\n到昨早我問佢知唔知尋晚咩事。<br />\n佢叫我離開佢屋企，以後唔好再去，<br />\n佢話佢好醜，係朋友面前吵都咁，仲要脫衫比我遮住。<br />\n我自己襯佢未醒前，縫返條裙，先有得著住走。<br />\n仲要佢話佢完全無內疚，整到我瘀曬最多比返醫藥費我。<br />\n<br />\n佢以前非常非常錫我，但佢話我成日發佢脾氣之後就開始冇晒耐性，有時我有少少唔鍾意，佢就會發翻我脾氣，但我從來冇諗過今次會發生咁嘅事。<br />\n我真係好唔開心，好失望，就算我話佢唔啱，佢邊有可能可以整到咁喎。我可以點做？我想知男仔覺得係咪真係學發咁大脾氣？"},{"pid":"1ca6cf89f0d2df3119c7160f0dd5c2e280d8415a","tid":812112,"uid":199902,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"未分嘅就分咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba79efe335a9c04a58f5b3565852b235e0e9567","tid":812112,"uid":199104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ca6cf89f0d2df3119c7160f0dd5c2e280d8415a","tid":812112,"uid":199902,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"未分嘅就分咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"分左了，但我好唔開心，從來無諗過佢好似變左第二個人咁"},{"pid":"0716cc6c3fdd12b3e694d326cb5bef32ea66f915","tid":812112,"uid":141645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:39:05.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"2dcd14ab4bf6427a8a8a94637ec144728af94d4a","tid":812112,"uid":66967,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"第時家暴都可能會 散啦屌 早走早著"},{"pid":"87c0a51acbfaeb5aee3eae518d54d46b08122b3b","tid":812112,"uid":20448,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:39:32.000Z","msg":"扯爛條裙都忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次同班fd一齊扯爛你d 衫衫褲褲輪完再打鳩你"},{"pid":"a992547405d557f513864656d189d1d03b701170","tid":812112,"uid":156547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:40:03.000Z","msg":"當你免費雞咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822f5c0e87c3d8c3d5157c78a974a489c2c9ad13","tid":812112,"uid":20448,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:41:10.000Z","msg":"不過男人老狗著裙仲要打底褲真係難頂左少少"},{"pid":"061f4b2e60efabe1377ebb029cfa9063149e9131","tid":812112,"uid":21249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:41:19.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得好假"},{"pid":"619f52e931cad3a719582543de7d1bd8fa1b01cd","tid":812112,"uid":199104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"87c0a51acbfaeb5aee3eae518d54d46b08122b3b","tid":812112,"uid":20448,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:39:32.000Z","msg":"扯爛條裙都忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次同班fd一齊扯爛你d 衫衫褲褲輪完再打鳩你"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"佢班朋友有部分有係咁叫佢同我道歉，<br />\n有部分覺得係我以前成日發佢脾氣，<br />\n佢先爆seed..加上醉左"},{"pid":"4258c9861efc9ef0f88536ff5491614d0278497b","tid":812112,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7e6beac870b99bd38e601277912bf3c23d6faa","tid":812112,"uid":78666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aba79efe335a9c04a58f5b3565852b235e0e9567","tid":812112,"uid":199104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ca6cf89f0d2df3119c7160f0dd5c2e280d8415a","tid":812112,"uid":199902,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"未分嘅就分咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"分左了，但我好唔開心，從來無諗過佢好似變左第二個人咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:42:27.000Z","msg":"以後帶眼識人啦<br />\n今次執返條命"},{"pid":"9914eb0e2e5c7542aadaf69e0c282c147f6f8826","tid":812112,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:43:14.000Z","msg":"絲打真係呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早走早著"},{"pid":"3dfc413a786f469f8a35c835f769b0deb7c872a5","tid":812112,"uid":199104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"822f5c0e87c3d8c3d5157c78a974a489c2c9ad13","tid":812112,"uid":20448,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:41:10.000Z","msg":"不過男人老狗著裙仲要打底褲真係難頂左少少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:43:25.000Z","msg":"我地女校出黎，大部分女仔都一定打底，師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d0bd310527ccf381a459d82b1ea0c96328bc8c","tid":812112,"uid":199104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9914eb0e2e5c7542aadaf69e0c282c147f6f8826","tid":812112,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:43:14.000Z","msg":"絲打真係呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早走早著"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:44:12.000Z","msg":"佢曾經真係非常愛錫我，所以我唔捨得"},{"pid":"70227f04eb4842b74958ea26300663c4e8aee9a8","tid":812112,"uid":126609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9f2b9e47bc72b32ccf53b66623547e6618b4939","tid":812112,"uid":110719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"搵個正經人家啦 <br />\n<br />\n又飲又醉 又亂發酒瘟<br />\n<br />\n比佢屌左幾多次啊 係佢心中 你都唔重要"},{"pid":"e0ac058d1a3095f0670c19bcebfcab6bc62e84c9","tid":812112,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:46:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好想比佢粗魯咁屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"0c15654e6eae3980308ba55485e943e8fb18672a","tid":812112,"uid":158585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"咁爛仔feel"},{"pid":"a82cb657660ff640c2c541035576b3c9d996e6ae","tid":812112,"uid":199104,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:47:22.000Z","msg":"我知我曾經做得唔夠好，係對佢好好但係一開始嘅時候會發小朋友脾氣。但係自從有一次佢同我講完之後，其實我一直都好努力改。真係有反省過自己去改，但逐漸見到佢嘅耐性已經不如以前，我話佢少少野，佢就已經發脾氣，嫌我煩。<br />\n<br />\n到底係唔係真係我一開始做得唔好，就唔會有機會有得改？我自問真係已經好努力改，點解唔可以一齊再努力行落去，點解佢要咁對我。"},{"pid":"494d825b89e4ba83f413a2d2bbb9844b96c1756f","tid":812112,"uid":61543,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:48:09.000Z","msg":"9撚成以前三日發一次條仔脾氣<br />\n然後嘈到咁上下你自己黑面走左去<br />\n久而久之積埋積埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bc7c249c2ad1da58a1496bbc9a18d68020a61d","tid":812112,"uid":199104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70227f04eb4842b74958ea26300663c4e8aee9a8","tid":812112,"uid":126609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:48:32.000Z","msg":"我好想原諒佢，但係佢都唔覺得自己錯，佢係班朋友面前有向我道歉，但走咗之後，第二朝就話我知佢一啲都冇內疚。"},{"pid":"15b839f50d8d0b4b1512362c34a52b97801214d1","tid":812112,"uid":199104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"494d825b89e4ba83f413a2d2bbb9844b96c1756f","tid":812112,"uid":61543,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:48:09.000Z","msg":"9撚成以前三日發一次條仔脾氣<br />\n然後嘈到咁上下你自己黑面走左去<br />\n久而久之積埋積埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"我認我係有發脾氣，但唔係成日。我對佢嘅好易唔係你能夠想像。<br />\n我病咗，不過我都煮飯入好遠俾佢，<br />\n知道佢經濟有困難，我二話不說借錢俾佢，<br />\n見到佢因為屋企有壓力喊，我自己都喊，<br />\n佢返工話肚餓，我第日即刻去買乾糧俾佢帶返工，<br />\n見佢有好多倒刺，我即刻去買護死皮油俾佢，<br />\n見佢話大腿有汗疹，我即刻買熱疹膏俾佢，<br />\n見佢話凍，我即刻除衫俾佢就算我着背心，<br />\n佢住得好遠，但我都成日搭到入黎搵佢。<br />\n親手用好多時間去到縫銀包，縫公仔俾佢。<br />\n有好多時間去整咭，整簿俾佢。<br />\n幫佢洗衫摺衫晾衫，執枱抹枱。<br />\n做佢嘅小秘書去提佢做每一件事。"},{"pid":"d60cdca32f51528f7dd85a9848ae52fa203dd110","tid":812112,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:52:29.000Z","msg":"唔通你拎發酒癲比佢做藉口咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係比大家時間冷靜下啦"},{"pid":"904faae0834d2daeb2d68755e66cd915cf3ea3cb","tid":812112,"uid":126609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}